sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (UI)
    participant T as Transact
    participant V as Contract Validator
    participant R as Router
    participant RT as Polyglot Runtime
    participant DB as DbClient
    participant RP as Repository
    participant L as Logger

    C->>T: POST /transact/api/transaction/execute
    T->>V: Validate payload against JSON schema
    V-->>T: OK / Errors
    T->>R: Route by contractId/version
    R->>RT: Invoke runtime (C#/Node/Python)
    RT->>DB: Execute dynamic SQL (XML)
    RT->>RP: File ops if needed
    RT-->>T: Standard DataSet result
    T->>L: Log request/response with GlobalID
    T-->>C: Response (DataSet / errors)
